dct_title_s: Bosnia and Herzegovina city graphic 1:10,000 : Bijeljina. Series M903
dct_description_sm: Alternate title: Bijeljina. In upper margin: WGS 84.Transverse Mercator projection. Relief shown by 5 meter contour intervals and spot elevations. Coordinate conversion WGS 84 to ED 50. This map falls within the NL 34-10, 1501,1:250,000 and 2884 II, 2984 III, 2984 IV, M709, 1:50,000. With a glossary, a guide to numbered features, a location map, and boundary guides.
